videos.description: Toledo gets off to a hot start as they strip  Bryce Singleton to force a fumble on the opening kickoff of the game.
videos.headline: Toledo forces fumble on opening kickoff

videos.description: Toledo takes advantage of the early turnover as Bryant Koback goes untouched for a 3-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Toledo RB walks in 3-yard TD

videos.description: FIU gets on the board as  Anthony Jones powers through Toledo defenders for a 6-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: FIU's Jones powers in for 6-yard TD

videos.description: FIU gets a big stop forcing a Toledo fumble on the 1 yard line.
videos.headline: FIU forces red-zone fumble from Toledo

videos.description: Christian Alexander connects with a wide-open Sterling Palmer for a 36-yard FIU touchdown.
videos.headline: FIU strikes back with 36-yard score

videos.description: Eli Peters escapes the pocket and finds a wide-open Jon'Vea Johnson for a 7-yard Toledo touchdown.
videos.headline: Toledo's Peters hits Johnson for 7-yard TD

videos.description: Anthony Jones eludes Toledo defenders for a 30-yard FIU touchdown, his second of the day.
videos.headline: FIU's Jones goes untouched for 30-yard TD

videos.description: Maurice Alexander finds the edge and breaks free for a 16-yard FIU touchdown.
videos.headline: FIU RB scampers in for 16-yard TD

videos.description: Toledo makes it a one-possession game as Eli Peters connects with Diontae Johnson for a 2-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Peters finds receiver for crucial Toledo TD

videos.description: Anthony Jones dashes up the middle for a 18-yard FIU touchdown.
videos.headline: FIU's Jones seals the game with 3rd TD

videos.description: FIU head coach Butch Davis discusses Anthony Jones' 3-TD performance and his recovery this season from a drive-by shooting in the summer of 2018.
videos.headline: Davis : it was 'tearful' watching Jones performance
